@startuml
title Data Flow of the Implemented AI-Assisted Knowledge System

skinparam style strictuml
skinparam shadowing false
top to bottom direction

skinparam rectangle {
  RoundCorner 8
}
skinparam ArrowColor #2f4f4f
skinparam ArrowThickness 1.2

actor "User" as User

rectangle "Upload API" as Upload
rectangle "Parser" as Parser
database "Workflow DB\n(SQLite)" as WFDB
rectangle "AI Suggestion Service\n(Ollama, Async Task)" as LLM
rectangle "Review & Approval" as Approval
folder "Raw KB\n(Markdown + YAML)" as KB
rectangle "KB Re-index Service" as Reindex
rectangle "Embedding Service\n(Ollama)" as Emb
database "Chroma Vector Store" as Chroma
rectangle "Knowledge Chat API" as Chat

User --> Upload : document
Upload --> Parser : raw input
Parser --> WFDB : normalized draft
WFDB --> LLM : suggestion input
LLM --> WFDB : updated suggestion
WFDB --> Approval : pending suggestion
Approval --> WFDB : decision
Approval --> KB : approved markdown
Approval --> Reindex : apply completed
Reindex --> Emb : chunks
Emb --> Chroma : vectors

User --> Chat : query
Chat --> Chroma : semantic search
Chroma --> Chat : chunks
Chat --> LLM : prompt + context
LLM --> Chat : answer
Chat --> User : answer + sources

note right of WFDB
Uploads, normalized text,
suggestions, reviews,
and applied changes
end note

note right of Chat
Vector-first retrieval with
lexical fallback when needed
end note

@enduml